## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all aspects of how behavioral problems affect development. The research is limited by the scope of the articles reviewed and the absence of recent studies beyond 2025. Additionally, individual differences in children mean that the impact of behavioral problems can vary widely, which may not be fully captured in the sources used.

